<view class="cu-card dynamic {{isCard?'no-card':''}}">
  <view class="cu-item shadow">
    <view class="text-content">
        折磨生出苦难，苦难又会加剧折磨，凡间这无穷的循环，将有我来终结！
    </view>
    <view class="grid flex-sub padding-lr {{isCard?'col-3 grid-square':'col-1'}}">
      <view class="bg-img {{isCard?'':'only-img'}}" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);" wx:for="{{isCard?9:1}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
      </view>
      <view class="solids-bottom padding-xs flex align-center">
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-gray text-sm text-right padding flex justify-between">
        <view class="cu-avatar sm radius margin-left" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big81005.jpg);"></view>
        <text class="text-right">凯尔 | R-Time：2019年12月3日</text>
        <view class="action">
          <text class="cuIcon-likefill margin-lr-xl "></text>
        </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>